text:
MAN MASTURBATED OPENLY IN HDB ESTATE   Wed, 01/02/2017 - 3:24pm Advertisement 
This morning (Feb 1), a man was seen touching his private parts in public at Block 78 at Redhill. 
The man was seated in front of a shop. He did not stop even thought there were passersby. 
Initially, the person who took the photo thought that the man had suffered a stroke until he saw the man's private parts. Editor's Note:
